These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, ritmeester
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy
2 different games are played: chess, scrabble
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the dancer##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
5. the mechanic is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
6. the person playing scrabble is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the person eating raspberry is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester   | old-henry      |
| Food          | strawberry | raspberry   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Job           | dancer     | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | drama       |
| Game   | chess    | scrabble        |
| Transport     | roller     | tram        |

